commit.title: Restore the use of git clone when locally running make ci-*.
commit.message:
Restore the use of git clone when locally running make ci-*.

This allows for a simpler workflow when preparing overlays.

We keep using tarballs on CI (or as soon as environment variable  is defined)
to reduce download bandwidth and latency.
